/static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132497214,imgsize-87984.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Warming seas are bringing octopus, red mullet and bream into UK waters]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132495526.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[As the seas warm, British waters are now seeing an influx of Mediterranean species. This environmental transformation is compelling local fishers to modify their traditional techniques. Notably, octopus populations are surging, impacting native shellfish and depleting other seafood supplies. In response, chefs are creatively revamping menus to highlight these new arrivals like octopus and bream, balancing the challenges with exciting culinary possibilities.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/warming-seas-are-bringing-octopus-red-mullet-and-bream-into-uk-waters-forcing-fishers-to-rethink-catches-and-chefs-to-learn-mediterranean-species/articleshow/132495526.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/warming-seas-are-bringing-octopus-red-mullet-and-bream-into-uk-waters-forcing-fishers-to-rethink-catches-and-chefs-to-learn-mediterranean-species/articleshow/132495526.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T20:48:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132496746,imgsize-228152.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Security hole’ enabled US-Israel bombing of Ayatollah’s residence: Iran minister Araghchi]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132496462.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iranian foreign minister Seyyed Abbas Araghchi alleged a security breach allowed foreign powers access.  This breach reportedly provided intelligence and influenced decision-making during a conflict.  He stated attackers knew Ayatollah Ali Khamenei's routine and targeted his residence precisely.  A regional leader had warned Iran about leadership being targeted before the conflict began.  Araghchi noted the foreign ministry remained operational throughout the intense 40-day war.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/security-hole-enabled-us-israel-bombing-of-ayatollahs-residence-iran-minister-araghchi/articleshow/132496462.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/security-hole-enabled-us-israel-bombing-of-ayatollahs-residence-iran-minister-araghchi/articleshow/132496462.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T20:45:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132496742,imgsize-61880.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['No bribes, no threats': Iran FM says US cannot scare people who expect death at any moment]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132496672.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/no-bribes-no-threats-iran-fm-says-us-cannot-scare-people-who-expect-death-at-any-moment/articleshow/132496672.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/no-bribes-no-threats-iran-fm-says-us-cannot-scare-people-who-expect-death-at-any-moment/articleshow/132496672.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T20:40:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132496708,imgsize-67394.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[DNA from 457 koalas suggests the species nearly went extinct 100,000 years ago, before humans...]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132494936.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Approximately 100,000 years ago, koalas faced near extinction due to brutal ice ages. A recent genetic study triumphantly highlights that this crisis occurred well before humans populated Australia. By examining koala genomes, scientists have beautifully illustrated how climate shifts triggered significant declines in their population. Presently, however, modern threats stem largely from human activities, underscoring the urgent need for dedicated conservation measures.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/dna-from-457-koalas-suggests-the-species-nearly-went-extinct-100000-years-ago-before-humans-reached-australia/articleshow/132494936.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/dna-from-457-koalas-suggests-the-species-nearly-went-extinct-100000-years-ago-before-humans-reached-australia/articleshow/132494936.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T19:07:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132495493,imgsize-305610.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['That's what Lindsey wanted': Trump seeks Iran's inclusion in Russia sanctions bill]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132496481.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump wants Republican lawmakers to add Iran to the Russia sanctions bill. This legislation targets major buyers of Russian energy and aims to hold them accountable. The revised bill refines tariff authority and adds new measures for sanctions evasion. It also incorporates acts targeting Chinese support for Russia's defense industry. The updated legislation seeks to prevent Tehran from acquiring nuclear weapons.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/thats-what-lindsey-wanted-trump-seeks-irans-inclusion-in-russia-sanctions-bill/articleshow/132496481.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/thats-what-lindsey-wanted-trump-seeks-irans-inclusion-in-russia-sanctions-bill/articleshow/132496481.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T20:19:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132496489,imgsize-892474.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Saudi Arabia records 22.5% rise in Umrah arrivals as over 1.27 million pilgrims visit kingdom]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132496296.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-records-22-5-rise-in-umrah-arrivals-as-over-1-27-million-pilgrims-visit-kingdom/articleshow/132496296.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-records-22-5-rise-in-umrah-arrivals-as-over-1-27-million-pilgrims-visit-kingdom/articleshow/132496296.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T20:12:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132496399,imgsize-1128168.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US envoy rejects Mamdani's threat to arrest Netanyahu during NYC visit]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132495773.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pure-political-theatre-us-envoy-rejects-zohran-mamdani