vation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/archaeologists-in-iraq-unearthed-a-rare-2600-year-old-assyrian-stele-of-king-ashurbanipal-at-ninevehs-shamash-gate-nearly-a-decade-after-isis-damaged-the-ancient-city/articleshow/132493986.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/archaeologists-in-iraq-unearthed-a-rare-2600-year-old-assyrian-stele-of-king-ashurbanipal-at-ninevehs-shamash-gate-nearly-a-decade-after-isis-damaged-the-ancient-city/articleshow/132493986.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T18:15:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132494761,imgsize-197842.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Canadian lawyer faces 6-month suspension for citing ChatGPT cases in court hearing]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132492065.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadian-lawyer-faces-6-month-suspension-for-citing-chatgpt-cases-in-court-hearing/articleshow/132492065.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadian-lawyer-faces-6-month-suspension-for-citing-chatgpt-cases-in-court-hearing/articleshow/132492065.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T15:31:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132492712,imgsize-491888.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Second attack in two days': Kuwait says Iran hit power, water desalination plant]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132491349.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></des