a site of myth and nature, seeks UNESCO World Heritage recognition.  This ancient Greek mountain is home to gods and diverse ecosystems.  Locals hope for global acknowledgment to ensure its continued protection.  The nomination process involves careful review and potential further requirements.  Recognition would bring responsibilities for preserving its unique cultural and natural values.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mount-olympus-the-mythological-home-of-zeus-and-the-ancient-greek-gods-is-being-considered-for-unesco-world-heritage-status-as-greece-seeks-protection-for-its-tallest-mountain/articleshow/132490953.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mount-olympus-the-mythological-home-of-zeus-and-the-ancient-greek-gods-is-being-considered-for-unesco-world-heritage-status-as-greece-seeks-protection-for-its-tallest-mountain/articleshow/132490953.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T12:27:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132490962,imgsize-165630.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is WardrobeWinter? Meet Plaqueboymax’s roommate at Kai Cenat’s Streamer University 2026]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132488765.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[WardrobeWinter became one of the biggest breakout creators from Kai Cenat’s Streamer University 2026. Already popular on TikTok and Twitch, he drew even more attention after his roommate clashes with Plaqueboymax. With help from counsellor YourRAGE, the two talked through their problems, agreed on simple ground rules and eventually ended the situation with a hug.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-wardrobewinter-meet-plaqueboymaxs-roommate-at-kai-cenats-streamer-university-2026/articleshow/132488765.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-wardrobewinter-meet-plaqueboymaxs-roommate-at-kai-cenats-streamer-university-2026/articleshow/132488765.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T05:31:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132488764,imgsize-831035.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US launches fresh airstrikes on Iran after attack on American troops in Jordan]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132488646.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[United States forces launched new airstrikes against Iran on President Donald Trump's orders.  These strikes aim to degrade Iran's ability to threaten commercial shipping.  The operation also retaliates for recent attacks on American service members in Jordan.  The US Central Command confirmed the military action began at 6 p.m. ET.  Iran has not yet issued any official comment on the developments.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-launches-fresh-airstrikes-on-iran-after-attack-on-american-troops-in-jordan/articleshow/132488646.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-launches-fresh-airstrikes-on-iran-after-attack-on-american-troops-in-jordan/articleshow/132488646.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T04:40:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132488668,imgsize-65043.cms"/></item></channel></rss>